{"tid":21013,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪欣囝囝兩度改名 張鎬濂跟後父闖娛圈","createTime":"2016-12-03T15:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T15:25:03.000Z","uid":26190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d26434f07df95754f8372c0a8e8ad313fef9be40","tid":21013,"uid":26190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"洪欣同莫少聰多年前愛得轟烈，洪欣仲未婚生咗囝囝莫鎬廉，近年洪欣改嫁張丹峰，囝囝索性跟後父姓，改名張浩鋒。最近浩鋒同後父張丹峰拍住上，拍內地嘅電視劇《致青春》，做張丹峰嘅童年版，好有camera face㗎。 <br />\n<br />\n浩鋒入行，開通微博同粉絲聯繫，生父莫少聰見有渠道同個仔聯絡，即時私信搵仔，雖然浩鋒微博俾面後父繼續用張姓，但個名用番「鎬濂」，原來洪欣個仔個名最初係用三點水嗰個「濂」㗎，唔通兩仔爺重修關係？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_457098_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_457098_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=39f10eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_457098_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&h=675eaf15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_457098_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine</a>"}]}